title: ESS的指令牌子用不了
author: omg_
txt_content:
如题，我这样输入 ：  [warp]                               主城
以前的服务器都是可以的，怎么办

replies.author: 梓
replies.txt_content:
ESS配置文件将warp前面的#删除 enabledSigns:   #- color   #- balance   #- buy   #- sell   #- trade   #- free   #- disposal   #- warp   #- kit   #- mail   #- enchant   #- gamemode   #- heal   #- info   #- spawnmob   #- repair   #- time   #- weather

复制代码

replies.author: 凯瑞
replies.txt_content: 搞个牌子命令插件就好了

replies.author: wu20011116
replies.txt_content: 把ess设置文件中warp一行前的#去掉即可
